---
title: Creamy Lamb Bolognese with Baby Spinach and Rigatoni
description: This quick and comforting lamb and spinach pasta bolognese requires just 15 minutes of hands-on cooking time. A rich and creamy lamb sauce is gently combined with wheat rigatoni to create this great heart warming dish to enjoy mid week!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lamb-bolognese-0429627c-b7b8d2ed.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/lamb-bolognese-5c24f971e3f339553c2dc4d2-41aa3337.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Italian
